sentences.en: The discovery in 1992 in the Vu Quang forests of two new, large mammal species made Vu Quang an area of internationally recognised biodiversity conservation value.

sentences.en: Speaking at the meeting, Vu Van Vien, director of Hanoi's transport department, voiced his support.
